  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your grill to medium heat.",
    "Brush the pitas with olive oil on both sides.",
    "Season with garlic powder and salt.",
    "Place the pitas on the grill and cook for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "Transfer the cooked pitas to a baking sheet.",
    "Top each pita with sliced jalapenos, a dollop of yogurt, and a sprinkle of parsley.",
    "Return the baking sheet to the grill and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until the cheese is melted and the pitas are crispy.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool for a few minutes before serving."
